                        <h4>How to set the Language in the Web User Interface?</h4>
                        <p class="justify">
                            The new INSTAR web interface for your ip camera detects automatically what default language your web browser is using. By default the web interface will be loaded in the language which is used by your web browser. You can also click <a href="/Web_User_Interface/1080p_Series/System/Language/">System / Language</a> for <strong>1080p cameras</strong>, or
                            <a href="/Web_User_Interface/720p_Series/Software/Language/">Software / Language</a>
